               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence</hi>. I said I knew nothing about the umbrellas, and randown a court; I was drunk, and resisted; they cut two wounds in my legand one in my shin; the doctor attended me twice; they tore my clothes somuch that they were obliged to give me these I have on. (<hi rend="italic">The prisoner hereshowed his leg, which teas dreadfully wounded, and he had two wounds on hishead</hi>.)</p>
